name: Union Square Nylon Tote
description:
Our new Union Square Nylon Tote offers sophisticated styling with smart details in a lightweight design. 

Made from double sided Italian nylon with a New York City theme seen in both the name and decorative cityscape printing on the lining of the bag. Leather trim throughout the bag provides structure including metal feet on the bottom. 

Gold personalization is available on a matching sewn leather patch, up to three initials. 

PLEASE BE SURE TO ORDER PERSONALIZATION IF YOU WOULD LIKE TO ADD UP TO 3 INITIALS.  PLEASE INDICATE THE INITIALS IN THE NOTES SECTION.

This is the essential tote for every season. 

Size: 141/2 W x 11 1/2”H x 6” D
Zip top closure for easy access
Exterior and interior slip pockets
Protective Metal feet
Handles with 10” drop
